name: Free Cross Platform UI Redesign
description:
Last year I wannted to redesign 100 unpopular apps to with cross platform design. Luckily I just did around 26 or so. Paid work comes my way and so I wanted to share my 24 UI's to reuse it remix and what not. 
Have fun with it and share it with me if you like (@bdnrzio)

Incuded redesign like last.fm, strava, sharezone, metro, debitoor, gyroscope and many more!
